Component_Description: Inactivity logout is behavior or policy-based and requires users to take physical action to log out when they are expecting inactivity longer than the defined period.
Profile_Description: Example Using NIST SP 800-53 Rev 5 Controls and SP 800-53A Rev 5 Assessment Procedures
